<p><b>Philip Pullman</b> <a href="/wiki/Order_of_the_British_Empire" title="Order of the British Empire">CBE</a> (born 19 October 1946) is an <a href="/wiki/England" title="England">English</a> <a href="/wiki/Novelist" title="Novelist" class="mw-redirect">writer</a>. He is the best-selling author of <i><a href="/wiki/His_Dark_Materials" title="His Dark Materials">His Dark Materials</a></i> (a trilogy of <a href="/wiki/Fantasy_fiction" title="Fantasy fiction" class="mw-redirect">fantasy</a> novels), and a number of other books.</p>
