<li>1995 <i><a href="/wiki/Clockwork_(novel)" title="Clockwork (novel)">Clockwork</a>, or, All Wound Up</i></li>
<li>1995 <i><a href="/wiki/The_Firework-Maker%27s_Daughter" title="The Firework-Maker's Daughter">The Firework-Maker's Daughter</a></i></li>
