<li>1999 <i><a href="/wiki/I_was_a_Rat!_or_The_Scarlet_Slippers" title="I was a Rat! or The Scarlet Slippers">I was a Rat! or The Scarlet Slippers</a></i></li>
<li>2000 <i>Puss in Boots: The Adventures of That Most Enterprising Feline</i></li>
<li>2004 <i><a href="/wiki/The_Scarecrow_and_his_Servant" title="The Scarecrow and his Servant">The Scarecrow and his Servant</a></i></li>
